    <sparkle:channel>beta</sparkle:channel>
    <description><![CDATA[
      <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 12px; }
        h3 { font-size: 14px; margin: 12px 0 6px 0; }
        h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
        ul { padding-left: 18px; margin: 4px 0; }
        li { margin: 4px 0; line-height: 1.5; }
      </style>
      <h3>Fixed</h3><ul> <li><b>Focus returns to previous app after capture</b> — closing the overlay (Escape, Enter, Cmd+C, etc.) now re-activates the previously focused application. No more click-to-refocus.</li> <li><b>Annotations preserved in beautified window snaps</b> — beautify + window snap captures now include annotations. Previously, annotations were lost because the beautify input used the raw window image without them.</li></ul>
    ]]></description>
